until we ruled out neurosyphilis.

18:52.841 --> 18:54.802
It's not neurosyphilis,
it's a PFO.

18:54.927 --> 18:58.347
It's neurosyphilis.
The tests were positive.

19:06.772 --> 19:09.441
It's always the same conversation.
They tell you you must be mistaken,

19:09.566 --> 19:13.028
which is why I always run the tests
twice. Then they blame the other guy.

19:13.153 --> 19:14.696
Which makes sense
if they're innocent.

19:14.822 --> 19:16.406
But, obviously,
half of them aren't.

19:16.532 --> 19:19.827
