busted. Scientifically proven.

19:19.952 --> 19:21.662
Unless your spouse
cheated, too.

19:21.787 --> 19:24.498
Exactly. That's what you're praying for
in that moment, that she cheated, too.

19:24.623 --> 19:26.625
And then, if she doesn't kill
you, you know that she did.

19:26.750 --> 19:28.126
You'd know she betrayed you.

19:28.252 --> 19:31.713
And then you realize
that that sucks worse.

19:35.759 --> 19:36.927
(CLEARS THROAT)

19:37.553 --> 19:38.929
The test must be wrong.

19:39.054 --> 19:40.931
I ran it twice.

19:41.056 --> 19:44.434
Not that test. The one
I took 10 years ago.

19:45.435 --> 19:47.938
What other explanation
is there?

19:58.115 --> 19:59.908
He really sees no
other possibility.

20:00.033 --> 20:01.910
Did you have an affair?

20:02.035 --> 20:02.870
No.

20:02.995 --> 20:04.746
Then why aren't you
angry with him?

20:09.251 --> 20:11.587
You ever know anybody
who's just too nice?

20:11.712 --> 20:13.672
- No.
- It's annoying.

20:13.881 --> 20:15.340
Then you realize it's annoying

20:15.465 --> 20:17.759
because they remind you
of what you're not,

20:17.885 --> 20:20.971
that you'll never be
as good as they are.

20:21.096 --> 20:24.600
And then you think,
why can't I?

20:24.725 --> 20:27.352
And before you know it,

20:27.477 --> 20:30.314
that naive idiot
you laughed at

20:32.065 --> 20:34.610
has made you
a better person.

20:36.361 --> 20:42.200
You really think I've been in love
all these years with a symptom?

20:42.910 --> 20:44.870
If syphilis caused
lesions in his brain,

20:44.995 --> 20:47.915
and the lesions
caused personality changes...

20:48.040 --> 20:51.710
