as his condition improves.

20:53.170 --> 20:55.923
I know my husband.
He's not going to change.

20:56.882 --> 20:59.051
You should get
yourself tested.

21:02.554 --> 21:04.264
So much for the bell curve.

21:04.389 --> 21:06.808
How can House be an ass
without it being an illness,

21:06.934 --> 21:08.810
but niceness is
a biological crime?

21:09.061 --> 21:10.771
You got five bucks?

21:10.896 --> 21:12.272
Yeah...

21:14.650 --> 21:18.779
Niceness just cost you five bucks,
being an ass generally turns a profit.

21:19.196 --> 21:22.866
Kutner, could you excuse us?
I need to do Taub's review.

21:22.991 --> 21:24.660
You can stay.

21:24.868 --> 21:27.371
I think it'd be better
if this was done privately.

21:27.496 --> 21:28.872
