21:28.997 --> 21:30.832
What is it with you guys?
I've given you advice before.

21:30.958 --> 21:32.292
Not as our boss.

21:32.417 --> 21:34.503
What's the difference?
Advice is advice.

21:34.711 --> 21:36.254
Fair enough. I'll go first.

21:36.380 --> 21:37.339
(CLEARS THROAT)

21:38.090 --> 21:40.592
"You demonstrate a great air of
confidence,

21:40.717 --> 21:42.052
which is really pissing me off."

21:42.177 --> 21:43.929
- House authorized me to...
- How long have you known him?

21:44.054 --> 21:45.472
- He's using you.
- I volunteered because

21:45.597 --> 21:46.473
- I knew he wouldn't...
- He could care less

21:46.598 --> 21:48.892
about the paperwork. He's using
you to screw with you.

21:49.017 --> 21:51.478
He knows it'll annoy us,
we'll stand up to you,

21:51.603 --> 21:52.896
which will force you
to confront the fact that

21:53.021 --> 21:54.272
even though you think
you're our superior,

21:54.398 --> 21:55.607
you're no different from us.

21:55.732 --> 21:59.069
He gave you authority,
to keep you in your place.

22:00.028 --> 22:03.407
- It's true.
- Thanks.

22:03.532 --> 22:04.408
Not him. What did he say?

22:04.533 --> 22:05.951
Nothing. What's true?

22:06.076 --> 22:07.786
If there's something
wrong with this guy,

22:07.911 --> 22:10.998
