to get me drunk?

22:20.090 --> 22:21.216
(WILSON CHUCKLES)

22:22.759 --> 22:24.594
- What time is it?
- 10:30.

22:24.720 --> 22:25.846
(EXCLAIMS)

22:26.054 --> 22:26.888
She'll kill you.

22:27.014 --> 22:29.433
