would have mentioned that to me.

22:49.703 --> 22:51.955
They told you? Wait.

22:52.080 --> 22:54.666
Why do you want
to get Amber angry?

22:54.791 --> 22:56.084
Because I'm your friend.

22:56.209 --> 22:58.128
No, no, no, you said
you approved.

22:58.253 --> 23:00.088
