you were taking the high road.

23:00.213 --> 23:01.923
For how long, the first exit?

23:02.049 --> 23:06.303
Hello, and thank you from saving me
from being righteous to death.

23:06.428 --> 23:07.679
<i>THIRTEEN:
Patient's vomiting blood.</i>

23:07.804 --> 23:08.847
Hematemesis could indicate...

23:08.972 --> 23:10.807
<i>HOUSE:
Don't put it on the board.</i>

23:10.932 --> 23:11.975
You don't think
it's a symptom?

23:12.100 --> 23:14.061
I think it's my marker.

23:14.186 --> 23:15.896
<i>HOUSE: He has syph and what?</i>

23:16.021 --> 23:18.482
And syph. It can
cause hematemesis.

23:18.607 --> 23:21.193
<i>Not everyone agrees.</i>

23:21.318 --> 23:22.611
How could you...

23:22.736 --> 23:24.571
<i>Because if you all thought
it was just syph</i>

23:24.696 --> 23:26.865
you wouldn't have woken me up
in the middle of the night.

23:26.990 --> 23:28.700
If it was just syph,
he wouldn't be getting worse.

23:28.825 --> 23:29.993
<i>He's already on penicillin.</i>

23:30.118 --> 23:31.620
The bleeding's probably
from liver damage,

23:31.745 --> 23:35.373
probably caused by ethanol in
the cleansers or the penicillin.

23:35.499 --> 23:38.210
