than I like to hear.

23:38.335 --> 23:40.754
Liver test and serologies,
are going to take a full day.

23:40.879 --> 23:42.464
Full night, actually.

23:42.589 --> 23:44.049
<i>Guy might not
make it to brunch.</i>

23:47.219 --> 23:50.639
Yes, I knew about
your issue with alcohol.

23:50.764 --> 23:52.808
