is that you knew as much as I did,

24:00.857 --> 24:04.778
and you're the one who's pouring down
the drinks. Why?

24:05.195 --> 24:07.656
Because I thought I was out
having fun with a friend.

24:07.781 --> 24:11.034
I didn't know the
drinks had subtext.

24:11.159 --> 24:14.162
I gotta get home.

24:17.374 --> 24:19.835
GGT's normal,
that rules out alcohol.

24:19.960 --> 24:21.336
