serum protein?

24:21.461 --> 24:22.546
It's positive.

24:23.296 --> 24:24.673
Kind of assumed
he had protein.

24:24.798 --> 24:26.800
It's how much protein
he has that we care about.

24:26.925 --> 24:28.718
He's positive for syphilis.

24:28.844 --> 24:31.513
Do you mind if I give you
a performance review?

24:31.638 --> 24:36.601
Not the patient. House.
He has syphilis.

24:44.526 --> 24:45.569
<i>What happened?</i>

24:46.611 --> 24:50.157
<i>Every time I searched my soul,
