25:31.865 --> 25:33.867
<i>MAN ON TV: Love lasts forever.</i>

25:39.331 --> 25:40.916
No, I don't.

25:41.041 --> 25:42.709
One of us found a vial of your blood
in the lab from when we...

25:42.834 --> 25:44.544
Which one of you?

25:44.669 --> 25:46.171
