because you like humiliating me.

30:31.498 --> 30:33.875
Wouldn't rule that
out completely.

30:34.000 --> 30:35.126
YOU busy?

30:35.251 --> 30:36.586
Almost done.

30:36.711 --> 30:43.134
So just remember, the rabbit goes around
the tree and jumps down the hole.

30:44.761 --> 30:46.930
Negative for sarcoidosis.

30:49.182 --> 30:50.975
Run him for everything
you can think of.

30:51.226 --> 30:55.855
Lepto, schisto, hemo and the fourth
Marx Brother nobody ever heard of.

30:57.857 --> 30:59.108
You bitch!

31:01.903 --> 31:04.155
I just went to get us some
lunch. You were asleep.

31:04.280 --> 31:06.074
You moved my book!

31:07.033 --> 31:09.702
Jeff, calm down,
it's just the drugs.

31:09.827 --> 31:12.455
The drugs didn't move my...

31:12.580 --> 31:13.456
(JEFF GASPS)

31:13.581 --> 31:15.083
Jeff?

31:15.208 --> 31:16.709
