allergic reaction.

32:15.685 --> 32:16.978
How does a fried liver
put him into a rage?

32:17.103 --> 32:19.480
It's not frying his liver,
it's frying his syphilis.

32:19.606 --> 32:22.317
The penicillin's working.
The real patient's emerging.

32:22.442 --> 32:26.070
